TYPE 3,20,10,40,NONE,Well, here we are again - another GRAAL release.
TYPE 3,20,10,50,NONE,Although perhaps not as big a leap forward as
TYPE 3,20,10,60,NONE,2.0 was compared to 1.2, I have still managed to
TYPE 3,20,10,70,NONE,add quite a nice bunch of major enhancements.
TYPE 3,20,10,85,NONE,Because the basic demo included in the delivery
TYPE 3,20,10,95,NONE,package can't be updated with all the new goodies
TYPE 3,20,10,105,NONE,for each release - my God, it would become a
TYPE 3,20,10,115,NONE,mess! - I felt a new issue of this very special
TYPE 3,20,10,125,NONE,disk mag was needed to fill the gap. It isn't
TYPE 3,20,10,135,NONE,very big, but then again, all it is here for is
TYPE 3,20,10,145,NONE,to tell you about and show off the new 2.1
TYPE 3,20,10,155,NONE,features. In fact, I hope you spend more time
